title: Best Dude On the Planet Matt Patricia Wears Goodell Clown Shirt Off Team Plane
text:
Best Dude On the Planet Matt Patricia Wears Goodell Clown Shirt Off Team Plane El Presidente | 
Click To Buy All Shirts 

I fucking love Matt Patricia. I fucking love him. Such a preposterous move to wear our Goodell Clown tshirt off the team plane. Mocking the man who days earlier said he didn’t know we existed. The first and most definitive shot at Roger Goodell by any member of the Pats. Matty P’s nuts just dragging on the ground here. I fucking love it. I love Matty Patricia. It’s gonna be a sad day when he gets his head coaching opportunity but nobody deserves it more than him.
